description: source_analyer is a simple code complexity source_file_counter without caring about the CC++ header files.It can deal with CC++Objective C  TNSDL code. It count the NLOC (lines of code without comments), CCN (cyclomatic complexity number) and token count of _functions.
longdescription: source_analyer is a simple code complexity source_file_counter without caring about the CC++ header files.It can deal with CC++Objective C  TNSDL code. It count the NLOC (lines of code without comments), CCN (cyclomatic complexity number) and token count of _functions.
